- initial version of multi-language-support
	The different languages are replaced when reading the resource-file.
They reside in a separate file (resource-base.rsl) with the
following structure:

entries: entry entries
entry: lang ':' count ':' text
lang: <two-characters>
count: '#' <three digits>
text: <string>

currently lang can only be set by the new config-variable lang, e.g.:
lang=it
